narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Great if you want to continue lessons for free and for a credit!
Take it if you want to maintain your vocal technique and keep up rep through the year! Important for any serious singer.

I would definitely recommend voice lessons for credit if you are a serious singer. My teacher was phenomenal and I feel I have grown immensely as a singer in this program. This program is really an incredible resource and I feel lucky to have been involved over the past two years.
